description:
Stuck on what to play or what to buy? Join TVGS as I list and discuss ten of the most over looked and obscure PSP hidden gems that deserve way more love. Many lesser known games have released for the Playstation portable handheld so let me know your choice of the top 10 overlooked games on the console down below! 

Join us on Discord - https://discord.gg/jkS7dGAdHY

All of my PSP videos can be found here - https://tinyurl.com/psp-video-list
